2026-03-20 22:17:08 | DEBUG    | src/search_service.py:300 | [Tavily] 原始响应: {'query': 'Enbridge Inc earnings revenue profit growth forecast', 'follow_up_questions': None, 'answer': None, 'images': [], 'results': [{'url': 'https://www.enbridge.com/stories/2026/march/record-financial-results-robust-outlook-exceptional-2025-for-enbridge', 'title': 'Record financial results, robust outlook: An exceptional 2025 for ...', 'content': 'Thanks to growing cash flows, Enbridge now has C$10 to C$11 billion available in annual investment capacity, said Enbridge Chief Financial Officer Pat Murray, which **supports investments in growth projects** across all four of our core business units. “Securing projects (with strong returns), combined with cost and revenue optimizations on existing assets, creates a compounding effect which will continue to grow our investment capacity into the future.”. ### Why invest in Enbridge? ## **C$14B in projects sanctioned as investment capacity grows**. Speaking of investment capacity, **Enbridge sanctioned a slate of projects in 2025 worth C$14 billion**, the largest single-year total in company history, while also placing C$5 billion worth of assets into service. All told, that means Enbridge now has a project backlog totaling C$39 billion, about C$8 billion of which we expect to place into service in 2026. “Today, our total secured backlog sits at $39 billion, up approximately 35% since Enbridge Day (our investor community conference in March 2025),” noted Mr. Ebel.', 'score': 0.9853, 'raw_content': None, 'from_cache': True}, {'url': 'https://www.insiderfinance.io/news/enbridge-earnings-beat-revenue-tops-forecasts', 'title': 'Enbridge Earnings Beat, Revenue Tops Forecasts | InsiderFinance', 'content': 'Enbridge earnings beat as Q4 adjusted EPS and revenue topped forecasts and the 10-K filing gives traders fresh disclosure to reassess guidance. (ENB) reported on Feb. 13, 2026, that fourth-quarter adjusted earnings per share (EPS) and revenue exce