入(ARPU)数据;虽提供了宽带用户数量,可同样未给出\nARPU\n数据。正因如此,KeyBanc\n认为根本无法据此推导出任何具有历史可比性的数据。周一,KeyBanc\n发表观点称:“我们认为当前最大的问题有两个:一是信息披露缺乏应有的透明度;二是数据缺乏可比性,这使得外界难以洞悉其业务转型的实际进展情况。”KeyBanc\n还觉得,Verizon\n必然是“精心挑选”了一些对其有利的指标进行公布,而将那些不利的指标悄悄隐藏了起来。与此同时,尽管\nVerizon\n同时公布了较为积极的财务指引,但这并未能平息市场的疑虑。根据\nVerizon\n披露的数据,其\n2025\n年无线及宽带业务的总收入达到了\n908.6\n亿美元。KeyBanc\n认为这一数据极为关键,原因是\nVerizon\n针对\n2026\n年同一业务指标给出', 'siteName': '新浪财经', 'siteIcon': 'https://th.bochaai.com/favicon?domain_url=https://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/hkstock/ggscyd/2026-03-17/doc-inhrhpmt8181807.shtml', 'datePublished': '2026-03-17T14:25:48+08:00', 'dateLastCrawled': '2026-03-17T14:25:48Z', 'cachedPageUrl': None, 'language': None, 'isFamilyFriendly': None, 'isNavigational': None}, {'id': 'https://api.bochaai.com/v1/#WebPages.4', 'name': 'Uzbekistan v Venezuela results, H2H stats | Soccer - Flashscore', 'url': 'https://www.flashscoreusa.com/game/soccer/uzbekistan-EZYKKRMc/venezuela-raj05RS9/', 'displayUrl': 'https://www.flashscoreusa.com/game/soccer/uzbekistan-EZYKKRMc/venezuela-raj05RS9/', 'snippet': 'Follow\nUzbekistan\nv\nVenezuela\nresults,\nh2h\nstatistics\nand\nUzbekistan\nlatest\nresults,\nnews\nand\nmore\ni', 'summary': 'Follow\nUzbekistan\nv\nVenezuela\nresults,\nh2h\nstatistics\nand\nUzbekistan\nlatest\nresults,\nnews\nand\nmore\ninformation.\nFlashscore\nsoccer\ncoverage\nincludes\nsoccer\nscores\nand\nsoccer\nnews\nfrom\nmore\nthan\n1000\ncompetitions\nworldwide.\nUzbekistan,\nVenezuela,\nReal\nMadrid,\nArsenal,\nChelsea,\nChampions\nLeague,\nCopa\nLibertadores,\nSerie\nA,\n...', 'siteName': 'www.flashscoreusa.com', 'siteIcon': 'https://th.bochaai.com/favicon?domain_url=https://www.flashscoreusa.com/game/soccer/uzbekistan-EZYKKRMc/venezuela-raj05RS9/', 'datePublished': '2026-03-14T16:59:37+08:00', 'dateLastCrawled': '2026-03-14T16:59:37Z', 'cachedPageUrl': None, 'language': None, 'isFamilyFriendly': None, 'isNavigational': None}, {'id': 'https://api.bochaai.com/v1/#WebPages.5', 'name': '三维通信管理层薪酬工资(002115.SZ)_财务报表分析 - 前瞻眼'